metadata.name: 0.0050 Staked JELLY/USDC SLP [2x Rewards]
metadata.description:
WARNING: Staking NFTs are a new type of Defi NFT and Opensea does not update staked position information in real time. 

##AMOUNTS (refresh Metadata to update)

 Staked JELLY/USDC SLP on last refresh was 0.0050

Unclaimed $JELLY rewards on last refresh was 250010

##Checks before trading

Staking NFTs are a new type of Defi NFT and the underlying asset value can change. For this reason, it is not recommended to put in future offers on these NFTs, safer to use buy now price. Note that the NFT owner is able to partially unstake in the Farm which will reduce the SLP staked in the NFT and they are able to claim the rewards. Before buying a Staking NFT, refresh the Metadata so you can see the latest updates on the value held. 

 ##Staking NFT [2x Rewards]
This NFT represents Staked JELLY/USDC SLP in the Royal Pool. When it is bought or sold, the value of the staked position is transferred to the new owner. 

##Royal Jelly Pool 
The Royal Jelly Pool is a whitelisted farm with exclusive 2X Bonus $JELLY rewards.  

##NFT holders 
This NFT can be traded freely on the secondary market like any other NFT, you can also transfer this NFT to a vault to keep your staked LPs safe. The NFT was minted by a whitelisted Royal Jelly at the time their LP tokens were staked. Any wallet holding this NFT gets access to Claim the rewards and Unstake the LP tokens without needing to be on the Royal Whitelist. But, only the whitelisted Royal Jellies can stake LPs in the Royal Pool. A wallet can hold multiple NFTs from the same pool and these display on the Jelly protocol UI as a cumulative staked balance of LPs. 

##Jelly Farming 
 Claim, Stake and Unstake from the Jelly Pools using Jelly Protocol at [https://app.jelly.io/farms/0xcC43331067234a0014d298b5226A1c22cb0ac66a](https://app.jelly.io/farms/0xcC43331067234a0014d298b5226A1c22cb0ac66a)
